How to generate a new version of pyrus
======================================

0. Be sure to be in pear2/all/ svn directory

1. Get the latest developer files
 $ php scripts/pyrus upgrade -p ../Pyrus_Developer/package.xml

2. Update package.xml
 $ php scripts/pyrus make

3. Create the phar
 $ php -dphar.readonly=0 scripts/pyrus package --phar
